{"tid":87093,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上報](勁冇品)tvb節目廣告盜用日本同人畫師圖片","createTime":"2017-01-19T14:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T16:02:06.000Z","uid":39181,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9136983b3b7e923bccb5aeb747dd457785a798","tid":87093,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"係高登見到依個POST，希望各位廣傳<br />\n雖然已經冇乜人睇TVB，但唔代表可以姑息依啲行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntvb節目 [1+1的幸福] 廣告中盜用日本同人畫師圖片(下圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmapYhaxQY7xQjmnu8VF4GrAWqWi2YwdT4QuCGJGnjMpJp?filename=K0892kL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0892kL.png&h=acdb3248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n調查下發現  圖中多張圖片均係出自一名日本畫師ki之手筆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=7123942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember.php%3Fid%3D7123942&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=368101b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=7123942</a><br />\n<br />\n圖片原址<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=54213822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember_illust.php%3Fmode%3Dmedium%26illust_id%3D54213822&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ad7ab11a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=54213822</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=51053830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember_illust.php%3Fmode%3Dmedium%26illust_id%3D51053830&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=65df1bf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=51053830</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=48226669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember_illust.php%3Fmode%3Dmedium%26illust_id%3D48226669&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c514fdee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=48226669</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=42037431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember_illust.php%3Fmode%3Dmedium%26illust_id%3D42037431&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=49ade2a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=42037431</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=56685097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fmember_illust.php%3Fmode%3Dmedium%26illust_id%3D56685097&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ebaaad5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=56685097</a><br />\n<br />\n聯絡ki後 得知對方完全不知道電視台於廣告中使用他繪畫的圖片  (對話如下)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s30.postimg.org/hhae9wb8h/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2Fhhae9wb8h%2Fimage.jpg&h=48df40bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n問:你好 我在香港tvb電視台節目《1+1的幸福》的電視宣傳廣告看見由你繪畫的圖片  請問你知不知道這件事?<br />\n<br />\n答: 你好。<br />\n不，我完全不知道<br />\n是怎樣的節目廣告呢?<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n上述對話  證實tvb電視台在原繪畫者ki不知情的狀況下 私自盜用了ki繪畫的插圖!<br />\n<br />\ntvB電視台偷圖惡行人神共憤 不能姑息 大家幫手將單野推上報公告天下  等全香港民眾知道tvB電視台既所作所為 為繪畫者討回公道!"},{"pid":"f953d75fba4e71d21ae1e6a4ad0f8b96d90d0b6a","tid":87093,"uid":67479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67d25b4fd624330b6191dc76f557cb63ef8441c2","tid":87093,"uid":14240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e00d3f15f46ef6a6ac08f6dd7d0a133424249f33","tid":87093,"uid":38464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"94ab3d0e6dad8a61ca6e4aa055b5f4c30bea8580","tid":87093,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"原來講呢壇 <br />\n繼某同類雜誌香港又衰一鑊"},{"pid":"6c752f0220dabd2148668f6528179f8db7ada880","tid":87093,"uid":35860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b15b54d530c733fcc239140802662ad2125fee","tid":87093,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"一国二制度一クオリティ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691b760e91b5a34263bc163c2c2198437b7bb8b8","tid":87093,"uid":31429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3cd4db6bd031f91c4cbefdce565667c0aef3be","tid":87093,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75f873a468e5d4e1093ad26be5fb75e50cb04b84","tid":87093,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問關tvb咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTvb節目喎"},{"pid":"d64602747eb506f83b7987d0d6eedccfad97b187","tid":87093,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問關tvb咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303d14a